name: Quan. Questions
data:
Regarding economic outlook in 2016, which of the following best describes your company approach to managing and executing digital marketing with clients? 
• We are increasing our digital investments
• We are decreasing our digital investments
• We are maintaining the status
• Economic doesn’t apply to us

• Budget spending trend in 2016
• Correlation of digital spending VS economic outlook

Please rank the percentage of increase for digital advertising spend at your space in year 2016?
0----------------------------100% <pls specifiy>

Which of the followings best describes most of your clients’ objectives for digital ad spend? 
• Brand awareness
• Sale 
• E-commerce channel
• Engagement
• PR
• CRM
• Etc. <pls specifiy>

How have your engagement models with clients changed over the last year?
• No change
• More project based work
• More retainer based work
• More education & training
• Embedding specialized resources at clients

What digital services, if any, do you expand in the past year & plan to expand in the first half of year 2016 that were previously handled by your external partners?
• A sampling of response
• Analytics
• SEO
• Email marketing
• SEM
• Social Listening
• Content creation & Video production
• Etc.
• Journey of full-service trend in digital industry?

How is your total media spending allocated across media in the first half of year 2016 (approximately)
• Digital
• Offline
